[Auction "S"]
1H pass 1NTpass3H pass 3H pass 4H pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{SOUTH has an above-minimum strength hand with a good 6-card suit. He opens 1

♥

.

NORTH, with 9 points, is a little too weak to bid at the 2-level so she bids a catchall 1NT.

SOUTH shows his 6-card suit and extra strength by jumping to 3

♥

, which

NORTH raises to 4

♥

since two trumps is now adequate support.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 2, chOption: S, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:2, nBasis: 2, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]

