[Deal "N:KQ74.83.762.AKQ2 A952.J2.AQ4.T953 JT83.AQ74.J53.76 6.KT965.KT98.J84"]
[Auction "N"]
1C pass 1H pass 1S pass 2S pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{NORTH has 14 points and opens her 4-card ♣ suit.

SOUTH must respond, and with two 4-card Majors bids them "up-the-line", saying 1

♥

.

NORTH now shows his 4-card ♠ suit, and SOUTH again must bid. Since SOUTH is pretty weak he just

raises to 2♠, which NORTH happily passes.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: N, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 0, nRot: 0, useStandardVul: true"]

