[Auction "S"]
pass pass 1S pass 3S pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{SOUTH has just 11 points, not enough to open the bidding.

But when NORTH opens 1♠ SOUTH should show her "almost opening strength"

by jumping to 3♠.

NORTH has just 13 points, and knowing SOUTH has less than 13 he passes.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 5, chOption: N, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 2, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]

